The '''Mosonszolnok Wind Farm''' is a [[wind farm]] in [[Győr-Moson-Sopron County]], [[Hungary]]. It has 12 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://www.ebrdrenewables.com/sites/renew/Lists/EBRD%20Master%20Spreadsheet/DispForm.aspx?ID=526&Source=http%3A%2F%2Febrdrenewables%2Ecom%2Fsites%2Frenew%2Fdefault%2Easpx Energy Corp built wind farm in Hódmezővásárhely, Hungary]</ref> with a nominal output of around 2 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 24 MW of power, enough to power over 9,494 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$40 million.

